2012年7月，洛德在家里花了半个小时写了〈贵族〉一曲<ref name="DailyBeast">{{cite web|last=Stern|first=Marlow|date=2013-07-22|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/07/22/meet-lorde-the-16-year-old-singer-poised-to-take-over-pop-music.html|title=Meet Lorde, the 16-Year-Old Singer Poised to Take Over Pop Music|publisher=The Daily Beast|accessdate=2013-11-24|archive-date=2017-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416211504/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/07/22/meet-lorde-the-16-year-old-singer-poised-to-take-over-pop-music.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name= BillboardQnA>{{cite web|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|date=2013-09-10|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5687330/lorde-qa-new-zealand-star-on-next-single-nicki-minaj-staying|title=Lorde Q&A: New Zealand Star On Next Single, Nicki Minaj & Staying Mysterious|work=Billboard|accessdate=2013-09-14|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6MNBmzxqH?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5687330/lorde-qa-new-zealand-star-on-next-single-nicki-minaj-staying|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两人在立特于[[奧克蘭_(紐西蘭)|奧克蘭]]莫宁赛德的黄金时代录音室录制歌曲<ref name="LittleLordeWork">{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11126667|title=Joel Little: Doing the Lorde's work|work=The New Zealand Herald|first=Lydia|last=Jenkin|date=2013-09-19|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6PzrBJBQX?url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119|archivedate=2014-06-01|access-date=2015-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。用了一周时间，洛德在学校放假期间完成〈贵族〉的录制<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/apr/11/joel-little-lorde|title=The secrets of Lorde's right-hand man, Joel Little|work=The Guardian|first=Huw|last=Oliver|date=2014-04-11|accessdate=2014-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015533/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/apr/11/joel-little-lorde|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛德看到1976年7月号的《[[国家地理_(杂志)|国家地理杂志]]》上摄影师泰德·斯皮格尔（{{lang|en|Ted Spiegel}}）所摄的一张图片，图片上的[[堪萨斯城皇家|堪萨斯城皇家]]队队员[[乔治·布列特|乔治·布列特]]穿着印有球队名的T恤衫，在棒球上签名，这让洛德萌生写歌讽刺流行音乐家奢华生活的想法<ref name="LyricalInfluences">{{cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zCSFHsd7NWA|title=Lyrical Influences (VEVO LIFT)|publisher=Vevo. YouTube|date=2013-11-27|others=Lorde|medium=video|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-date=2014-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140215060040/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zCSFHsd7NWA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年9月3日接受[[VH1|VH1]]采访时，洛德回忆道：“这就是那个词的来源，这真的很酷。”更广泛地说，历史悠久的贵族也是歌曲的灵感之一<ref name = "VH1 Inspiration">{{cite web| last= O'Keefe| first= Meghan| date= 2013-09-03| url= http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2013-09-03/vh1-you-oughta-know-lorde/| title= VH1 You Oughta Know Artist Lorde Explains What Being 'Royal' Means To Her| publisher= VH1| accessdate= 2013-09-14| archive-date= 2015-06-27| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150627024048/http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2013-09-03/vh1-you-oughta-know-lorde/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。她还解释歌词“在梦里我们也可以开[[凯迪拉克|凯迪拉克]]”（{{lang|en|We're driving Cadillacs in our dreams}}）是她在12岁时收到的一本日记中读到的<ref name="LyricalInfluences"/>。洛德进一步透露，她在创作过程中受到嘻哈派艺术家“胡扯”地提到“昂贵”的酒精和汽车的影响<ref>{{cite web| title= NZ Music Sensation, Lorde, Releases First Music Video For 'Royals'| url= http://thediplomat.com/asia-life/2013/05/nz-music-sensation-lorde-releases-first-music-video-for-royals/| work= The Diplomat| accessdate= 2013-08-12| date= 2013-05-15| archive-date= 2013-10-24| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131024075901/http://thediplomat.com/asia-life/2013/05/nz-music-sensation-lorde-releases-first-music-video-for-royals/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

