〈贵族〉使用[[Pro_Tools|Pro Tools]]软件制作<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://issuu.com/redbulletin.com/docs/1213_nz_lowres/44|title=December 2013|page=44|journal=The Red Bulletin|first=Robert|last=Tighe|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319095741/https://issuu.com/redbulletin.com/docs/1213_nz_lowres/44|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Spin|Spin]]》杂志一名专栏作家形容歌曲是一首[[艺术流行|艺术流行]]歌曲<ref name="spin"/>。与此同时，《[[声音效果|声音效果]]》的评论员形容歌曲是小众作品<ref>{{cite web |title= Listen: Raekwon remixes Lorde's 'Royals' |url= http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/11/listen-raekwon-remixes-lordes-royals/ |accessdate= 2014-07-08 |publisher= Consequence of Sound |date= 2013-11-05 |archive-date= 2015-04-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150426173526/http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/11/listen-raekwon-remixes-lordes-royals/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，而《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的詹姆斯·拉楚（{{lang|en|James Lacho}}）详述歌曲是一首电子流行乐作品<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite news|title=Lorde – New Music|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|accessdate=2013-09-14|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2013-09-01|first=James|last=Lachno|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131709/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/new-music/10296479/Lorde-New-Music.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲以D{{le|混合利底亚调式|Mixolydian mode}}写就，紧贴I-vii-IV（D-c-G）{{le|和弦进程|chord progression}}。歌曲有着每分钟85拍（行板）的舒缓节拍<ref name = "sheetmusic">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtdFPE.asp?ppn=MN0121796|title=Lorde 'Royals' Sheet Music|publisher=Musicnotes.com. EMI Music Publishing|accessdate=2014-06-10|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101002402/http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtdFPE.asp?ppn=MN0121796|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲旋律编入{{le|响指声|Finger snapping}}和贝斯<ref name="Idolator">{{cite web| last= Lansky| first= Sam| date= 2013-04-29| url= http://idolator.com/7455428/pop-goes-the-world-meet-little-nikki-tove-lo-suvi-laurel-lorde/6| title= Pop Goes The World: Meet Little Nikki, Tove Lo, Suvi, Laurel & Lorde| publisher= Idolator| accessdate=2013-09-14}}</ref>。洛德在演唱歌曲用的是在[[F♯_(音名)|F♯3]]到F♯5之间的[[次女高音|次女高音]]音域<ref name="GlobeAndMail">{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/music/album-reviews/in-an-age-of-manufactured-stars-lorde-is-a-refreshing-change/article14678181 |title=In an age of manufactured stars, Lorde is a refreshing change |first=Brad |last=Wheeler |date=2013-10-07 |work=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-date=2013-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008105358/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/music/album-reviews/in-an-age-of-manufactured-stars-lorde-is-a-refreshing-change/article14678181 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="sheetmusic"/>。歌曲歌词关注当代艺人的奢靡生活方式。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的布拉德·惠勒（{{lang|en|Brad Wheeler}}）表示，歌曲表达出对嘻哈艺人“宝石迷阵般的生活节奏”的不以为然：“但歌词里总说着：金牙、美酒、浴室里吸毒”（{{lang|en|But every song’s like gold teeth, Grey Goose, trippin’ in the bathroom}}）<ref name="GlobeAndMail"/>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的保罗·莱斯特称歌曲主题好比《爱情俱乐部EP》（{{lang|en|''The Love Club EP''}}）的〈百万美元钞票〉（{{lang|en|"Million Dollar Bills"}}）和《[[纯粹女英雄|纯粹女英雄]]》的〈[[网球场_(歌曲)|网球场]]〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/jun/07/new-band-lorde|title=New band of the day: Lorde (No 1,582)|work=The Guardian|date=2013-06-07|first=Paul|last=Lester|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033124/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/jun/07/new-band-lorde|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
歌曲获得影评人的广泛赞誉。[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]给予歌曲四星评价（满分五星），称赞歌曲的“让人印象深刻的上瘾叠句在它的质朴上茁壮成长”<ref name = "Digital Spy">{{cite web |last=Corner |first=Lewis |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/review/a516418/lorde-royals-single-review.html#ixzz2fFcTSsgL |title=Lorde: 'Royals' - Single review |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2013-09-18 |accessdate=2013-09-19 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164053/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/review/a516418/lorde-royals-single-review.html#ixzz2fFcTSsgL |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而其他评价则褒贬不一，《单曲点唱机》（{{lang|en|''The Singles Jukebox''}}）的评价为3分到8分（满分10）<ref name = "Singles Jukebox">{{cite web|title=Lorde - Royals|url=http://www.thesinglesjukebox.com/?p=7333|work=The Singles Jukebox|accessdate=2013-09-26|archive-date=2018-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729230610/http://www.thesinglesjukebox.com/?p=7333|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的邓肯·格里夫（{{lang|en|Duncan Greive}}）给予将歌曲正面评价的重点放在洛德的声线表现和歌曲歌词内容上。他写道：“制作过程多余且令人难忘，人声不知何故同时表现得脆弱且专横，但歌曲的歌词推动歌曲在英国和美国榜上登顶”，还称赞歌曲对浪费和财富的“直接抨击”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/global/2013/nov/08/lordes-song-royals-deserves-nuanced-critique |title=Lorde's song Royals deserves nuanced critique |first=Duncan |last=Greive |work=The Guardian |date=2013-11-08 |accessdate=2014-04-19 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427041229/https://www.theguardian.com/global/2013/nov/08/lordes-song-royals-deserves-nuanced-critique |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

歌曲被众多媒体认定为2013年最好的歌曲之一。《[[Spin|Spin]]》在它的年度50佳歌曲榜单中，将歌曲列入第15位，并评论称：“真正的艺术流行乐很少有这样的自我宣扬”<ref name= spin>{{cite web| url=http://www.spin.com/articles/best-songs-2013/?slide=36| title=50 Best Songs of 2013: #15 – Lorde: 'Royals'| work=Spin| accessdate=2013-06-10| archive-date=2014-10-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021191930/http://www.spin.com/articles/best-songs-2013/?slide=36| dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》作家道格拉斯·沃尔克（{{lang|en|Douglas Wolk}}）写道：“歌曲尖锐反对强加给资本主义受害者的愿望”，将歌曲放在他的2013年十佳歌曲榜的第十位<ref name= time>{{cite web| url= http://entertainment.time.com/2013/12/04/arts-and-entertainment/slide/top-10-songs/| title= Top 10 Songs| work= Time| date= 2013-12-04| first= Douglas| last= Wolk| accessdate= 2013-12-08| archive-date= 2015-03-24| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150324094417/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/12/04/arts-and-entertainment/slide/top-10-songs/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。与此同时，《声音效果》的将歌曲列入年度最佳歌曲<ref>{{cite web| url= http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/12/songs-of-the-year-2013/| title= Top 50 Songs of 2013| work= Consequence of Sound| accessdate= 2013-12-06| archive-date= 2013-12-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131206211045/http://consequenceofsound.net/2013/12/songs-of-the-year-2013/| dead-url= no}}</ref>，《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》将其列入年度第二佳单曲<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-best-songs-of-2013-20131204/lorde-royals-19691231| title= 100 Best Songs of 2013| work= Rolling Stone| accessdate= 2013-12-08| archive-date= 2018-06-27| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180627202647/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-best-songs-of-2013-20131204/lorde-royals-19691231| dead-url= no}}</ref>。2013年12月18日，《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》编辑杰森·利普舒茨（{{lang|en|Jason Lipshutz}}）、艾丽卡·拉米雷斯（{{lang|en|Erika Ramirez}}）和布拉德·威特（{{lang|en|Brad Wete}}）将歌曲提名为年度第三佳歌曲<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/list/5840322/20-best-songs-of-2013-critics-picks?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=photo&utm_campaign=photo-vs-link&list_page=1| title= Best Songs of 2013: Critics' Picks| work= Billboard| author= Billboard Staff| date= 2013-12-18| accessdate= 2013-12-19| archive-date= 2019-02-14| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190214065936/https://www.billboard.com/articles/list/5840322/20-best-songs-of-2013-critics-picks?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=photo&utm_campaign=photo-vs-link&list_page=1| dead-url= no}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》杂志将歌曲列入2013年最佳歌曲榜单的第20位<ref>{{cite web| url= http://entertainment.time.com/2013/12/20/the-25-best-songs-of-2013-the-entire-year/slide/no-20-royals-lorde/| title= The 25 Best Songs of 2013| work= Time| date= 2013-12-20| access-date= 2016-07-12| archive-date= 2021-01-26| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210126225623/https://entertainment.time.com/2013/12/20/the-25-best-songs-of-2013-the-entire-year/slide/no-20-royals-lorde/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。《{{le|乡村之声|The Village Voice}}》的{{le|Pazz & Jop|Pazz & Jop}}年度评论员投票将歌曲列入2013年最佳歌曲榜的第二位，紧随[[蠢朋克|蠢朋克]]的〈[[幸運星_(傻瓜龐克歌曲)|-{zh-cn:幸运儿; zh-tw:幸運星; zh-hant:Get Lucky; zh-sg:Get Lucky; zh-mo:Get Lucky}-]]〉之后。

2013年10月15日，联合创作人[[洛德_(歌手)|艾拉·叶里奇-奥康纳]]和[[喬爾·立特|喬爾·立特]]赢得表彰新西兰原创歌曲的{{le|2013年APRA银卷轴奖|2013 APRA Silver Scroll Awards}}<ref name="3news.co.nz">{{cite news |url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Lordes-Silver-Scroll-a-big-deal-for-co-writer-Joel-Little/tabid/418/articleID/317408/Default.aspx |title=Lorde's Silver Scroll 'a big deal' for co-writer Joel Little |work=3 News |publisher=MediaWorks New Zealand |date=2013-10-16 |access-date=2016-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015235413/http://www.3news.co.nz/Lordes-Silver-Scroll-a-big-deal-for-co-writer-Joel-Little/tabid/418/articleID/317408/Default.aspx |archive-date=2013-10-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Lorde takes out top Silver Scroll">{{cite news |url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/national/224792/lorde-takes-out-top-silver-scroll |title=Lorde takes out top Silver Scroll |publisher=Radio New Zealand |date=2013-10-16 |accessdate=2016-07-12 |archive-date=2014-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010063802/http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/national/224792/lorde-takes-out-top-silver-scroll |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[第56届格莱美奖|第56届格莱美奖]]上，歌曲赢得{{le|格莱美奖年度唱片奖|Grammy Award for Record of the Year|年度唱片}}、{{le|格莱美奖年度歌曲奖|Grammy Award for Song of the Year|年度歌曲}}和{{le|格莱美奖年度最佳流行个人演出|Grammy Award for Best Pop Solo Performance|最佳流行个人演出}}三项提名。歌曲最终赢得后两项奖<ref name= billboard1>{{cite web| url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5819883/grammy-awards-2014-full-nominations-list-complete-nominees| title= Grammy Awards 2014: Full Nominations List| work= Billboard| date= 2013-12-06| accessdate= 2013-12-16| archive-date= 2015-12-10| archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6dfpmpzyN?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5819883/grammy-awards-2014-full-nominations-list-complete-nominees| dead-url= no}}</ref>。歌曲还在{{le|2013年新西兰音乐奖|2013 New Zealand Music Awards}}上赢得年度歌曲奖<ref>{{cite news|title=Lorde wins big at 2013 NZ Music Awards|url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Lorde-wins-big-at-2013-NZ-Music-Awards/tabid/418/articleID/322318/Default.aspx|accessdate=2013-11-21|work=3 News|publisher=MediaWorks New Zealand|date=2013-11-21|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202231355/http://www.3news.co.nz/Lorde-wins-big-at-2013-NZ-Music-Awards/tabid/418/articleID/322318/Default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 音乐录影带 ==
歌曲官方录影带由乔尔·科法利（{{lang|en|Joel Kefali}}）执导<ref>{{cite web|url=//www.clipland.com/Summary/701014121/|title=Lorde "Royals" (2013)|publisher=clipland.com|access-date=2021-05-18|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927140025/http://www.clipland.com/Summary/701014121/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2013年5月12日在洛德的YouTube官方频道发布<ref>{{YouTube|LFasFq4GJYM|LORDE - Royals}}</ref>，美国版则于2013年6月18日在她的[[Vevo|Vevo]]帐号上发布<ref>{{YouTube|nlcIKh6sBtc|Lorde - Royals (US Version)}}</ref>。和歌曲主题一致，视频大多由普通青少年慢动作做平常事情的镜头组成。视频演员是洛德的同学。国际版还附上洛德唱歌的镜头，但洛德自己很少在视频中亮相。她这样解释自己没亮相的原因：“对我而言，音乐录影带就像创造一件艺术品，我想让它有电影的感觉，像一件让你自己沉浸其中的作品。让我参与其中没有必要。所以我只是稍微出现在里头，但我觉得这很不错<ref name="huff">{{cite web|last=Michelson|first=Noah|title=Lorde, 16-Year-Old New Zealand Musician, Talks 'Royals' Video, Feminism And More|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/lorde-interview_n_3644831.html|work=Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-08-10|date=2013-07-24|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://archive.is/20131014184950/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/24/lorde-interview_n_3644831.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

美国版采用了跟国际版相同的片段，但穿插了更多洛德唱歌的镜头。开头和结束的画面被省略，暗喻洛德的另外两首歌曲。这个剪辑将时长从4分2秒缩减到3分21秒。美国版获得了3亿次观看的认证等级，并在{{le|2013年新西兰音乐奖|2013 New Zealand Music Awards}}上赢得最佳录影带奖<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11160876 |title=Lorde, Aaradhna win big at music awards (+photos) |work=The New Zealand Herald |publisher=APN News & Media |date=2013-11-22 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108175539/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11160876 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。视频在[[2014年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2014年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]上赢得“最佳摇滚视频”奖，当时视频获得3.87亿观看，截至2016年7月，累计观看次数已超过6亿次。

《纯粹女英雄》于2014年2月在日本发行时，洛德与日本插画家兼音乐人Akiakane联袂歌曲动画版音乐录影带<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.universal-music.co.jp/lorde/news/2014/01/20/ |title=全米9週NO.1! グラミー賞有力候補の17歳歌姫、ロード。日本の人気女性クリエイター秋赤音とコラボ実現! |trans_title=US Billboard No. 1! Promising 17 year old Grammy candidate, Lorde. Collaborating with popular Japanese female creator Akane Aki! |publisher=Universal Music Japan |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121001630/http://www.universal-music.co.jp/lorde/news/2014/01/20/ |date=2014-01-20 |archivedate=2014-01-21 |accessdate=2014-01-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 现场表演 ==
2013年8月13日，歌曲重制版在{{le|KCRW|KCRW}}电台节目《{{le|多彩早晨|Morning Becomes Eclectic}}》上现场录制<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/event/music/211655048/kcrw-presents-lorde |title=KCRW Presents: Lorde |date=2013-08-13 |publisher=NPR |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KUrIqWPE?url=http://www.npr.org/event/music/211655048/kcrw-presents-lorde |archivedate=2013-10-19 |access-date=2013-10-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年10月1日，洛德首次在《{{le|吉米·法伦深夜秀|Late Night with Jimmy Fallon}}》献上歌曲的美国电台荧屏首秀，当时她身着白裙，有键盘手和鼓手伴奏。〈白牙少年〉（{{lang|en|"White Teeth Teens"}}）也在节目中表演，但只在网上播出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/lorde-plays-it-cool-with-royals-on-fallon-20131002 |title=Lorde Plays It Cool With 'Royals' on 'Fallon' |first=Erin |last=Coulehan |work=Rolling Stone |date=2013-10-02 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2013-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205171658/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/lorde-plays-it-cool-with-royals-on-fallon-20131002 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/10/02/lorde-royals-fallon/ |title=Watch Lorde make her American TV debut on Fallon |first=Ray |last=Rahman |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2013-10-02 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2015-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121114650/http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/10/02/lorde-royals-fallon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。后来她于2013年10月4日的[[VH1|VH1]]电视节目《{{le|早晨活力现场秀|Big Morning Buzz Live}}》演唱了这首歌，当时她衣着黑色高领毛衣和裙子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2013-10-04/lorde-royals-big-morning-buzz-live |title=Lorde Graces VH1's ''Big Morning Buzz Live'' With A 'Royals' Performance |first=Meghan |last=O'Keefe |publisher=VH1 |date=2013-10-04 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2015-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720181825/http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2013-10-04/lorde-royals-big-morning-buzz-live/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2013/10/04/lorde-royals-big-morning-buzz-live-video/ |title=Lorde Performed 'Royals' On 'Big Morning Buzz Live,' Has The No. 1 Song In The Country + Put Out An Album. So, Yeah, Her Week Ruled. |first=John |last=Walker |publisher=MTV |date=2013-10-04 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014181832/http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2013/10/04/lorde-royals-big-morning-buzz-live-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年10月9日，她在美国访谈节目《[[艾伦秀|艾伦秀]]》上表演该曲<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2013/10/09/lorde-performs-royals-on-ellen/ |title=Lorde Performs 'Royals' on Ellen |work=Rap-Up |date=2013-10-09 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012040916/http://www.rap-up.com/2013/10/09/lorde-performs-royals-on-ellen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。洛德用歌曲为2013年新西兰音乐奖开场<ref>{{cite news |title=Official Programme – Run of Show |at=lift-out booklet: p. 14 |work=The New Zealand Herald |publisher=APN News & Media |date=2013-11-21}}</ref>。2014年1月，洛德在[[第56届格莱美奖|第56届格莱美奖]]上演唱该曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.directlyrics.com/watch-56th-annual-grammy-awards-the-performances-news.html|title=56th Annual Grammy Award Performances|date=|work=Direct Lyrics|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2018-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205134750/https://directlyrics.com/watch-56th-annual-grammy-awards-the-performances-news.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在{{le|2014年全英音乐奖|2014 Brit Awards}}上，洛德与[[解密兄弟|解密兄弟]]联袂奉献歌曲[[电音|电音]]版<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/the-brit-awards/news/disclosure-perform-with-lorde-alunageorge-at-the-brits-2014 |title=Disclosure Perform With Lorde, AlunaGeorge At The BRITs 2014Disclosure Perform With Lorde, AlunaGeorge At The BRITs 2014 |work=MTV News |publisher=MTV UK |date=2014-02-19 |accessdate=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807002332/http://www.mtv.co.uk/the-brit-awards/news/disclosure-perform-with-lorde-alunageorge-at-the-brits-2014 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11205847 |title=Lorde's Brit award a 'priceless surprise' |work=The New Zealand Herald |publisher=APN News & Media |date=2014-02-20 |accessdate=2014-02-20 |archive-date=2020-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907210043/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11205847 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲和之后的〈{{lang|en|White Noise}}〉于2014年2月19日由全英音乐奖在iTunes Stores发布<ref name="RWN">{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/royals-white-noise-live-from/id823938215 |title=Royals / White Noise (Live from the BRITs) [feat. AlunaGeorge] - Single |publisher=iTunes Store (Apple Inc) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225215429/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/royals-white-noise-live-from/id823938215 |archivedate=2014-02-25 |access-date=2014-04-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲销售收益将捐给{{le|战争儿童|War Child (charity)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2014/02/watch-lorde-and-disclosure-team-up-at-2014-brit-awards/ |title=Watch: Lorde and Disclosure team up for 'Royals' remix at 2014 Brit Awards |first=Alex |last=Young |publisher=Consequence of Sound |date=2014-02-20 |accessdate=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2014-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220001701/http://consequenceofsound.net/2014/02/watch-lorde-and-disclosure-team-up-at-2014-brit-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]上名列第72位<ref name="Official Singles Chart UK Top 100">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/singles-chart/ |title=Official Singles Chart UK Top 100 |date=2014-03-01 |publisher=Official Charts Company |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68FSyzVqr?url=http://www.officialcharts.com/singles-chart/ |archivedate=2012-06-07 |access-date=2014-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

